Package robocup.managers

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommandsManager
    This class will send command about robots velocities and action to the grSim
    DetectionManager
    DetectionManager class is used to receive the conditions of game objects from the grSim and as a start point of the the loop
    GameManager
    This class control every other class and connect them to get into the result
    MovementManager
    This class can change robots velocity and rotation velocity according to StrategyManager calls
    StrategyManager
    This class will manage game planning and machine learning
